#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Datasource health check"
msgstr "数据源健康检查"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you use the link:https://quarkus.io/extensions/io.quarkus/quarkus-smallrye-health[`quarkus-smallrye-health`] extension, the `quarkus-agroal` and reactive client extensions automatically add a readiness health check to validate the datasource."
msgstr "如果您使用了 link:https://quarkus.io/extensions/io.quarkus/quarkus-smallrye-health[quarkus-smallrye-health] 扩展 `，quarkus-agroal` 和 reactive client 扩展会自动添加一个就绪性健康检查，以验证数据源。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When you access your application’s health readiness endpoint, `/q/health/ready` by default, you receive information about the datasource validation status.\n"
"If you have multiple datasources, all datasources are checked, and if a single datasource validation failure occurs, the status changes to `DOWN`."
msgstr "当您访问应用程序的健康状态就绪端点（默认地址为 `/q/health/ready` ）时，会收到有关数据源验证状态的信息。如果您有多个数据源，系统会检查所有数据源；如果其中任何一个数据源验证失败，状态将变为 `DOWN` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can disable this behavior by setting `quarkus.datasource.health.enabled=false`."
msgstr "您可以通过将 `quarkus.datasource.health.enabled` 设置为 `false` 来禁用此行为。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To exclude only a particular datasource from the health check:"
msgstr "若要仅将特定数据源从健康检查中排除："

#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Datasource metrics"
msgstr "数据源指标"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When you add the xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[`quarkus-micrometer`] extension, `quarkus-agroal` can publish datasource metrics to the metrics registry.\n"
"To enable these metrics, set `quarkus.datasource.metrics.enabled=true`."
msgstr "添加 xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[quarkus-micrometer] 扩展后， `quarkus-agroal` 即可将数据源指标发布到指标注册表。要启用这些指标，请将 `quarkus.datasource.metrics.enabled` 设置为 `true` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For the published metrics to report values, Agroal must enable its internal metrics collection.\n"
"By default, Agroal enables internal metrics collection for all datasources when a metrics extension is present and `quarkus.datasource.metrics.enabled` is set to `true`."
msgstr "为了使已发布的指标能够报告数值，Agroal 必须启用其内部指标收集功能。默认情况下，当存在指标扩展且 `quarkus.datasource.metrics.enabled` 设置为 `true` 时，Agroal 会为所有数据源启用内部指标收集功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To disable metrics for a specific datasource, set `quarkus.datasource.jdbc.metrics.enabled=false`.\n"
"For a named datasource, set `quarkus.datasource.<datasource name>.jdbc.metrics.enabled=false`.\n"
"This setting stops internal metrics collection and stops exposing datasource metrics at the `/q/metrics` endpoint."
msgstr "要禁用特定数据源的指标，请将 `quarkus.datasource.jdbc.metrics.enabled` 设置为 `false` 。 对于命名数据源，请将 `quarkus.datasource.<数据源名称>.jdbc.metrics.enabled 设置为 false` 。此设置将停止内部指标收集，并停止在 `/q/metrics` 端点上暴露数据源指标。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To enable internal metrics collection explicitly for the default data source, set `quarkus.datasource.jdbc.metrics.enabled=true`.\n"
"To enable internal metrics collection explicitly for a named data source, set `quarkus.datasource.<datasource name>.jdbc.metrics.enabled=true`.\n"
"This enables internal metrics collection even when you do not add a metrics extension.\n"
"You can access the collected metrics programmatically by calling `dataSource.getMetrics()` on an injected `AgroalDataSource` instance."
msgstr "要为默认数据源显式启用内部指标收集，请将 `quarkus.datasource.jdbc.metrics.enabled` 设置 `为 true` 。要为指定名称的数据源显式启用内部指标收集，请将 `quarkus.datasource.<数据源名称>.jdbc.metrics.enabled 设置为 true` 。 即使未添加指标扩展，此设置也会启用内部指标收集。您可以通过在注入的 `AgroalDataSource` 实例上调用 `dataSource.getMetrics()` ，以编程方式访问收集到的指标。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When metrics collection is disabled for a data source, all metric values are zero."
msgstr "当某数据源的指标收集功能被禁用时，所有指标值均为零。"

