msgstr "默认情况下，只跟踪 SQL 语句的执行。从数据源获取连接 `（` 调用 `getConnection()` ）不会被跟踪。要同时跟踪连接获取，请显式启用："

#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/datasource.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Narayana transaction manager integration"
